Package: cubature
Type: Package
Title: Adaptive Multivariate Integration over Hypercubes
Version: 2.0.4.2
VignetteBuilder: knitr
SystemRequirements: GNU make
URL: https://bnaras.github.io/cubature/
BugReports: https://github.com/bnaras/cubature/issues
